docs.abstract: Without clear policy goals, the first lady has relied on the power of her brand to spread Be Best’s message. Her supporters think that’s enough.
docs.snippet: Without clear policy goals, the first lady has relied on the power of her brand to spread Be Best’s message. Her supporters think that’s enough.
docs.lead_paragraph: WASHINGTON — Without concrete policy goals, Melania Trump has spent the past year relying on the power of her image to spread the message of “Be Best,” her child-focused platform dedicated to kindness and well being. Celebrating the first year of the program in the Rose Garden on Tuesday, her supporters made it clear that this was enough.

headline.main: Melania Trump Celebrates, With Superlatives, ‘Be Best’ Campaign
headline.print_headline: First Lady Celebrates, in Superlatives, Her ‘Be Best’ Campaign

docs.abstract: President Trump says that his protectionist trade policies have accelerated economic growth, but little evidence supports that claim.
docs.snippet: President Trump says that his protectionist trade policies have accelerated economic growth, but little evidence supports that claim.
docs.lead_paragraph: President Trump threatened over the weekend to re-escalate his trade war with China by raising tariffs on nearly all Chinese imports. He implied that the move would not hurt the American economy and said that the tariffs he has already imposed “are partially responsible for our great economic results” in the United States.

headline.main: Are Trump’s Tariffs Bolstering the U.S. Economy? Nope
